PrecisAppointment of CHRISTOPHER GIBBINS as Consul General of Canada in Chandigarh (Republic of India); PIERRE GIROUX as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Suriname, with residence in Georgetown; KUMAR GUPTA as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Botswana, with residence in Harare; and JORDAN REEVES as Consul General of Canada in Mumbai (Republic of India).
